          "cookies": [],
          "content": {
            "size": 18591,
            "mimeType": "application/json",
            "compression": 15147,
            "text": "[{\"error\":false,\"data\":{\"conversations\":[{\"id\":30615,\"name\":\"\",\"subname\":null,\"imageurl\":null,\"type\":1,\"membercount\":2,\"ismuted\":false,\"isfavourite\":false,\"isread\":true,\"unreadcount\":null,\"members\":[{\"id\":759,\"fullname\":\"Juan Carlos Calloni\",\"profileurl\":\"https:\\/\\/frsfco.cvg.utn.edu.ar\\/user\\/profile.php?id=759\",\"profileimageurl\":\"https:\\/\\/frsfco.cvg.utn.edu.ar\\/theme\\/image.php\\/adaptable\\/core\\/1769817503\\/u\\/f1\",\"profileimageurlsmall\":\"https:\\/\\/frsfco.cvg.utn.edu.ar\\/theme\\/image.php\\/adaptable\\/core\\/1769817503\\/u\\/f2\",\"isonline\":false,\"showonlinestatus\":true,\"isblocked\":false,\"iscontact\":false,\"isdeleted\":false,\"canmessageevenifblocked\":true,\"canmessage\":true,\"requirescontact\":false,\"cancreatecontact\":true,\"contactrequests\":[]}],\"messages\":[{\"id\":116819,\"useridfrom\":5135,\"text\":\"<p>Buen d\\u00eda profe, quer\\u00eda saber si estar\\u00e1n los parciales para ver hoy o qu\\u00e9 d\\u00eda podremos verlos en su defecto. Desde ya muchas gracias y aguardo su respuesta!<\\/p>\",\"timecreated\":1779982698}],\"candeletemessagesforallusers\":false},{\"id\":30372,\"name\":\"\",\"subname\":null,\"imageurl\":null,\"type\":1,\"membercount\":2,\"ismuted\":false,\"isfavourite\":false,\"isread\":true,\"unreadcount\":null,\"members\":[{\"id\":771,\"fullname\":\"Silvana Armando\",\"profileurl\":\"https:\\/\\/frsfco.cvg.utn.edu.ar\\/user\\/profile.php?id=771\",\"profileimageurl\":\"https:\\/\\/frsfco.cvg.utn.edu.ar\\/pluginfile.php\\/1540\\/user\\/icon\\/adaptable\\/f1?rev=1\",\"profileimageurlsmall\":\"https:\\/\\/frsfco.cvg.utn.edu.ar\\/pluginfile.php\\/1540\\/user\\/icon\\/adaptable\\/f2?rev=1\",\"isonline\":false,\"showonlinestatus\":true,\"isblocked\":false,\"iscontact\":false,\"isdeleted\":false,\"canmessageevenifblocked\":true,\"canmessage\":true,\"requirescontact\":false,\"cancreatecontact\":true,\"contactrequests\":[]}],\"messages\":[{\"id\":115619,\"useridfrom\":771,\"text\":\"<p>Hola Felipe. S\\u00ed, todo bien. S\\u00ed, not\\u00e9 que lo subi\\u00f3 \\u00e9l y ya te hab\\u00eda registrado la entrega. Gracias por avisar.<\\/p>\",\"timecreated\":1778082022}],\"candeletemessagesforallusers\":false},{\"id\":21719,\"name\":\"\",\"subname\":null,\"imageurl\":null,\"type\":1,\"membercount\":2,\"ismuted\":false,\"isfavourite\":false,\"isread\":true,\"unreadcount\":null,\"members\":[{\"id\":1241,\"fullname\":\"Laura Rivara\",\"profileurl\":\"https:\\/\\/frsfco.cvg.utn.edu.ar\\/user\\/profile.php?id=1241\",\"profileimageurl\":\"https:\\/\\/frsfco.cvg.utn.edu.ar\\/pluginfile.php\\/3150\\/user\\/icon\\/adaptable\\/f1?rev=420625\",\"profileimageurlsmall\":\"https:\\/\\/frsfco.cvg.utn.edu.ar\\/pluginfile.php\\/3150\\/user\\/icon\\/adaptable\\/f2?rev=420625\",\"isonline\":false,\"showonlinestatus\":true,\"isblocked\":false,\"iscontact\":false,\"isdeleted\":false,\"canmessageevenifblocked\":true,\"canmessage\":true,\"requirescontact\":false,\"cancreatecontact\":true,\"contactrequests\":[]}],\"messages\":[{\"id\":111046,\"useridfrom\":1241,\"text\":\"<p>Estimados Estudiantes, en la secci\\u00f3n EVALUACIONES, debajo de la tarea, se encuentra un archivo con el CRONOGRAMA de las exposiciones para ma\\u00f1ana y para el d\\u00eda martes 25\\/11.<br>\\nEl d\\u00eda de ma\\u00f1ana utilizaremos el aula 117 y el d\\u00eda martes 25\\/11 el aula 119.<br>\\n<br>\\nSaludos cordiales<br>\\nLaura Rivara <\\/p>\",\"timecreated\":1763500311}],\"candeletemessagesforallusers\":false},{\"id\":20951,\"name\":\"\",\"subname\":null,\"imageurl\":null,\"type\":1,\"membercount\":2,\"ismuted\":false,\"isfavourite\":false,\"isread\":true,\"unreadcount\":null,\"members\":[{\"id\":848,\"fullname\":\"Gabriela Ribotta\",\"profileurl\":\"https:\\/\\/frsfco.cvg.utn.edu.ar\\/user\\/profile.php?id=848\",\"profileimageurl\":\"https:\\/\\/frsfco.cvg.utn.edu.ar\\/pluginfile.php\\/2018\\/user\\/icon\\/adaptable\\/f1?rev=1118999\",\"profileimageurlsmall\":\"https:\\/\\/frsfco.cvg.utn.edu.ar\\/pluginfile.php\\/2018\\/user\\/icon\\/adaptable\\/f2?rev=1118999\",\"isonline\":false,\"showonlinestatus\":true,\"isblocked\":false,\"iscontact\":false,\"isdeleted\":false,\"canmessageevenifblocked\":true,\"canmessage\":true,\"requirescontact\":false,\"cancreatecontact\":true,\"contactrequests\":[]}],\"messages\":[{\"id\":107313,\"useridfrom\":5135,\"text\":\"<p>Buenas tardes, profesora. Ten\\u00eda una duda respecto a la exposici\\u00f3n de los temas: \\u00bfma\\u00f1ana continuamos con las exposiciones o retomamos las clases normales? En caso de continuar, \\u00bfqu\\u00e9 grupos deber\\u00edan exponer? Muchas gracias y aguardo su respuesta.<\\/p>\",\"timecreated\":1761079531}],\"candeletemessagesforallusers\":false},{\"id\":22169,\"name\":\"\",\"subname\":null,\"imageurl\":null,\"type\":1,\"membercount\":2,\"ismuted\":false,\"isfavourite\":false,\"isread\":true,\"unreadcount\":null,\"members\":[{\"id\":1243,\"fullname\":\"Vale Giletta\",\"profileurl\":\"https:\\/\\/frsfco.cvg.utn.edu.ar\\/user\\/profile.php?id=1243\",\"profileimageurl\":\"https:\\/\\/frsfco.cvg.utn.edu.ar\\/pluginfile.php\\/3152\\/user\\/icon\\/adaptable\\/f1?rev=14057\",\"profileimageurlsmall\":\"https:\\/\\/frsfco.cvg.utn.edu.ar\\/pluginfile.php\\/3152\\/user\\/icon\\/adaptable\\/f2?rev=14057\",\"isonline\":false,\"showonlinestatus\":true,\"isblocked\":false,\"iscontact\":false,\"isdeleted\":false,\"canmessageevenifblocked\":true,\"canmessage\":true,\"requirescontact\":false,\"cancreatecontact\":true,\"contactrequests\":[]}],\"messages\":[{\"id\":91800,\"useridfrom\":1243,\"text\":\"<p>Estudiantes<br>\\n<br>\\nYa se encuentran disponibles las notas del segundo parcial en la secci\\u00f3n contrato pedag\\u00f3gico. <br>\\n<br>\\nQuienes deseen revisar el parcial, estar\\u00e1n disponibles el Martes 19\\/11 de 18 a 19 (aula a definir). <br>\\n<br>\\nPor otra parte, quienes est\\u00e9n en condiciones y deseen realizar recuperatorio de algunos de los parciales, les solicitamos que se inscriban en el siguiente formulario que estar\\u00e1 disponible hasta el jueves 21\\/11. <br>\\n<br>\\nhttps:\\/\\/forms.gle\\/rDLxc9NJvWPAefTG7<br>\\n<br>\\nEl recuperatorio se realizar\\u00e1 el Lunes 25\\/11 a las 18:00 (en un s\\u00f3lo turno)<br>\\n<br>\\nQuedamos a disposici\\u00f3n para consultas. <br>\\n<br>\\nSaludos cordiales<br>\\n<br>\\nLa c\\u00e1tedra de estad\\u00edstica<\\/p>\",\"timecreated\":1731756673}],\"candeletemessagesforallusers\":false},{\"id\":21619,\"name\":\"\",\"subname\":null,\"imageurl\":null,\"type\":1,\"membercount\":2,\"ismuted\":false,\"isfavourite\":false,\"isread\":true,\"unreadcount\":null,\"members\":[{\"id\":868,\"fullname\":\"Juan Pablo Ferreyra\",\"profileurl\":\"https:\\/\\/frsfco.cvg.utn.edu.ar\\/user\\/profile.php?id=868\",\"profileimageurl\":\"https:\\/\\/frsfco.cvg.utn.edu.ar\\/theme\\/image.php\\/adaptable\\/core\\/1769817503\\/u\\/f1\",\"profileimageurlsmall\":\"https:\\/\\/frsfco.cvg.utn.edu.ar\\/theme\\/image.php\\/adaptable\\/core\\/1769817503\\/u\\/f2\",\"isonline\":false,\"showonlinestatus\":true,\"isblocked\":false,\"iscontact\":false,\"isdeleted\":false,\"canmessageevenifblocked\":true,\"canmessage\":true,\"requirescontact\":false,\"cancreatecontact\":true,\"contactrequests\":[]}],\"messages\":[{\"id\":91423,\"useridfrom\":868,\"text\":\"<p>Hola, buenas noches<br>\\nya sub\\u00ed feedback del TPI, cualquier cosa me avisan<br>\\nsaludos<\\/p>\",\"timecreated\":1731370419}],\"candeletemessagesforallusers\":false},{\"id\":24019,\"name\":\"\",\"subname\":null,\"imageurl\":null,\"type\":1,\"membercount\":2,\"ismuted\":false,\"isfavourite\":false,\"isread\":true,\"unreadcount\":null,\"members\":[{\"id\":1242,\"fullname\":\"Romina Karlich\",\"profileurl\":\"https:\\/\\/frsfco.cvg.utn.edu.ar\\/user\\/profile.php?id=1242\",\"profileimageurl\":\"https:\\/\\/frsfco.cvg.utn.edu.ar\\/pluginfile.php\\/3151\\/user\\/icon\\/adaptable\\/f1?rev=14213\",\"profileimageurlsmall\":\"https:\\/\\/frsfco.cvg.utn.edu.ar\\/pluginfile.php\\/3151\\/user\\/icon\\/adaptable\\/f2?rev=14213\",\"isonline\":false,\"showonlinestatus\":true,\"isblocked\":false,\"iscontact\":false,\"isdeleted\":false,\"canmessageevenifblocked\":true,\"canmessage\":true,\"requirescontact\":false,\"cancreatecontact\":true,\"contactrequests\":[]}],\"messages\":[{\"id\":89845,\"useridfrom\":1242,\"text\":\"<p>Buenos d\\u00edas! <br>\\nPara un mejor aprovechamiento de la clase de Probabilidad y Estad\\u00edstica del d\\u00eda de hoy, se recomienda acudir con notebook o dispositivo similar que disponga de Microsoft Excel. <br>\\nNos vemos en la clase.<br>\\nSaludos<\\/p>\",\"timecreated\":1730123501}],\"candeletemessagesforallusers\":false},{\"id\":23975,\"name\":\"\",\"subname\":null,\"imageurl\":null,\"type\":1,\"membercount\":2,\"ismuted\":false,\"isfavourite\":false,\"isread\":true,\"unreadcount\":null,\"members\":[{\"id\":865,\"fullname\":\"Valeria Cavallero\",\"profileurl\":\"https:\\/\\/frsfco.cvg.utn.edu.ar\\/user\\/profile.php?id=865\",\"profileimageurl\":\"https:\\/\\/frsfco.cvg.utn.edu.ar\\/pluginfile.php\\/1973\\/user\\/icon\\/adaptable\\/f1?rev=698514\",\"profileimageurlsmall\":\"https:\\/\\/frsfco.cvg.utn.edu.ar\\/pluginfile.php\\/1973\\/user\\/icon\\/adaptable\\/f2?rev=698514\",\"isonline\":false,\"showonlinestatus\":true,\"isblocked\":false,\"iscontact\":false,\"isdeleted\":false,\"canmessageevenifblocked\":true,\"canmessage\":true,\"requirescontact\":false,\"cancreatecontact\":true,\"contactrequests\":[]}],\"messages\":[{\"id\":89655,\"useridfrom\":865,\"text\":\"<p>Alumno:  Diaz Aimar, Felipe<br>\\n Paso resumen de notas:<br>\\n\\u2022\\tPr\\u00e1cticos 1:9<br>\\n\\u2022\\tPr\\u00e1ctico 2: 8<br>\\n<br>\\n\\u2022\\tPromedio pr\\u00e1cticos: 9<br>\\n\\u2022\\tParcial 1: 10<br>\\n\\u2022\\tParcial 2 :ausente<br>\\n<br>\\n<br>\\nNOTA: deb\\u00e9s recuperar el 2do parcial para obtener la regularidad o la promoci\\u00f3n.  Consulta en calendario (en ppt de clase) la fecha del recuperatorio. <br>\\nCualquier duda, comun\\u00edcate conmigo. <br>\\nSlds.  <br>\\nValeria<\\/p>\",\"timecreated\":1729807055}],\"candeletemessagesforallusers\":false},{\"id\":23112,\"name\":\"\",\"subname\":null,\"imageurl\":null,\"type\":1,\"membercount\":2,\"ismuted\":false,\"isfavourite\":false,\"isread\":true,\"unreadcount\":null,\"members\":[{\"id\":860,\"fullname\":\"Diego Cocconi\",\"profileurl\":\"https:\\/\\/frsfco.cvg.utn.edu.ar\\/user\\/profile.php?id=860\",\"profileimageurl\":\"https:\\/\\/frsfco.cvg.utn.edu.ar\\/pluginfile.php\\/1953\\/user\\/icon\\/adaptable\\/f1?rev=2258273\",\"profileimageurlsmall\":\"https:\\/\\/frsfco.cvg.utn.edu.ar\\/pluginfile.php\\/1953\\/user\\/icon\\/adaptable\\/f2?rev=2258273\",\"isonline\":false,\"showonlinestatus\":true,\"isblocked\":false,\"iscontact\":false,\"isdeleted\":false,\"canmessageevenifblocked\":true,\"canmessage\":true,\"requirescontact\":false,\"cancreatecontact\":true,\"contactrequests\":[]}],\"messages\":[{\"id\":84095,\"useridfrom\":860,\"text\":\"<p>Resultado 3er parcial --&gt; Pr\\u00e1ctica: 8.35, Total: 9 (nueve), Promoci\\u00f3n. RECUPERATORIO: Pr\\u00e1ctica 1er parcial<\\/p>\",\"timecreated\":1719608988}],\"candeletemessagesforallusers\":false},{\"id\":22698,\"name\":\"\",\"subname\":null,\"imageurl\":null,\"type\":1,\"membercount\":2,\"ismuted\":false,\"isfavourite\":false,\"isread\":true,\"unreadcount\":null,\"members\":[{\"id\":3231,\"fullname\":\"Vanina Fraire\",\"profileurl\":\"https:\\/\\/frsfco.cvg.utn.edu.ar\\/user\\/profile.php?id=3231\",\"profileimageurl\":\"https:\\/\\/frsfco.cvg.utn.edu.ar\\/pluginfile.php\\/16281\\/user\\/icon\\/adaptable\\/f1?rev=741872\",\"profileimageurlsmall\":\"https:\\/\\/frsfco.cvg.utn.edu.ar\\/pluginfile.php\\/16281\\/user\\/icon\\/adaptable\\/f2?rev=741872\",\"isonline\":false,\"showonlinestatus\":true,\"isblocked\":false,\"iscontact\":false,\"isdeleted\":false,\"canmessageevenifblocked\":true,\"canmessage\":true,\"requirescontact\":false,\"cancreatecontact\":true,\"contactrequests\":[]}],\"messages\":[{\"id\":82312,\"useridfrom\":3231,\"text\":\"<p>ATENCI\\u00d3N MENSAJE PARA COMISI\\u00d3N DE LOS VIERNES: el pr\\u00f3ximo Viernes 24\\/5 deber\\u00e1n asistir ambas comisiones a las 16.00 al Aula 115. Saludos<\\/p>\",\"timecreated\":1716427164}],\"candeletemessagesforallusers\":false},{\"id\":20952,\"name\":\"\",\"subname\":null,\"imageurl\":null,\"type\":1,\"membercount\":2,\"ismuted\":false,\"isfavourite\":false,\"isread\":true,\"unreadcount\":null,\"members\":[{\"id\":433,\"fullname\":\"Claudio Carrizo\",\"profileurl\":\"https:\\/\\/frsfco.cvg.utn.edu.ar\\/user\\/profile.php?id=433\",\"profileimageurl\":\"https:\\/\\/frsfco.cvg.utn.edu.ar\\/pluginfile.php\\/696\\/user\\/icon\\/adaptable\\/f1?rev=2794853\",\"profileimageurlsmall\":\"https:\\/\\/frsfco.cvg.utn.edu.ar\\/pluginfile.php\\/696\\/user\\/icon\\/adaptable\\/f2?rev=2794853\",\"isonline\":false,\"showonlinestatus\":true,\"isblocked\":false,\"iscontact\":false,\"isdeleted\":false,\"canmessageevenifblocked\":true,\"canmessage\":true,\"requirescontact\":false,\"cancreatecontact\":true,\"contactrequests\":[]}],\"messages\":[{\"id\":77012,\"useridfrom\":5135,\"text\":\"<p>Hola profesor, yo no he podido asistir a el 4to parcial para aprobaci\\u00f3n directa ya que me encontraba en C\\u00f3rdoba debido a un problema m\\u00e9dico. Espero pueda entender y si es necesario presentar un certificado para poder rendirlo normalmente comun\\u00edquemelo por favor. Muchas gracias y aguardo su respuesta!<\\/p>\",\"timecreated\":1701269477}],\"candeletemessagesforallusers\":false},{\"id\":19333,\"name\":\"\",\"subname\":null,\"imageurl\":null,\"type\":1,\"membercount\":2,\"ismuted\":false,\"isfavourite\":false,\"isread\":true,\"unreadcount\":null,\"members\":[{\"id\":847,\"fullname\":\"Mar\\u00eda Laura L\\u00f3pez\",\"profileurl\":\"https:\\/\\/frsfco.cvg.utn.edu.ar\\/user\\/profile.php?id=847\",\"profileimageurl\":\"https:\\/\\/frsfco.cvg.utn.edu.ar\\/pluginfile.php\\/2017\\/user\\/icon\\/adaptable\\/f1?rev=3623510\",\"profileimageurlsmall\":\"https:\\/\\/frsfco.cvg.utn.edu.ar\\/pluginfile.php\\/2017\\/user\\/icon\\/adaptable\\/f2?rev=3623510\",\"isonline\":false,\"showonlinestatus\":true,\"isblocked\":false,\"iscontact\":false,\"isdeleted\":false,\"canmessageevenifblocked\":true,\"canmessage\":true,\"requirescontact\":false,\"cancreatecontact\":true,\"contactrequests\":[]}],\"messages\":[{\"id\":77010,\"useridfrom\":5135,\"text\":\"<p>Hola profesora, yo no he podido asistir a el 4to parcial para aprobaci\\u00f3n directa ya que me encontraba en C\\u00f3rdoba debido a un problema m\\u00e9dico. Espero pueda entender y si es necesario presentar un certificado para poder rendirlo normalmente comun\\u00edquemelo por favor. Muchas gracias y aguardo su respuesta!<\\/p>\",\"timecreated\":1701269241}],\"candeletemessagesforallusers\":false},{\"id\":20814,\"name\":\"\",\"subname\":null,\"imageurl\":null,\"type\":1,\"membercount\":2,\"ismuted\":false,\"isfavourite\":false,\"isread\":true,\"unreadcount\":null,\"members\":[{\"id\":1422,\"fullname\":\"Luana Genero\",\"profileurl\":\"https:\\/\\/frsfco.cvg.utn.edu.ar\\/user\\/profile.php?id=1422\",\"profileimageurl\":\"https:\\/\\/frsfco.cvg.utn.edu.ar\\/pluginfile.php\\/3388\\/user\\/icon\\/adaptable\\/f1?rev=3466346\",\"profileimageurlsmall\":\"https:\\/\\/frsfco.cvg.utn.edu.ar\\/pluginfile.php\\/3388\\/user\\/icon\\/adaptable\\/f2?rev=3466346\",\"isonline\":false,\"showonlinestatus\":true,\"isblocked\":false,\"iscontact\":false,\"isdeleted\":false,\"canmessageevenifblocked\":true,\"canmessage\":true,\"requirescontact\":false,\"cancreatecontact\":true,\"contactrequests\":[]}],\"messages\":[{\"id\":75143,\"useridfrom\":1422,\"text\":\"<p>Hola Felipe buenas tardes.<br>\\n<br>\\nNo pod\\u00e9s promocionar la teor\\u00eda y no la pr\\u00e1ctica. Las condiciones son PROMOCION DE TP o APROBACI\\u00d3N DIRECTA. Saludos!<\\/p>\",\"timecreated\":1699482069}],\"candeletemessagesforallusers\":false},{\"id\":19777,\"name\":\"\",\"subname\":null,\"imageurl\":null,\"type\":1,\"membercount\":2,\"ismuted\":false,\"isfavourite\":false,\"isread\":true,\"unreadcount\":null,\"members\":[{\"id\":2564,\"fullname\":\"Sonia Dalmazzo\",\"profileurl\":\"https:\\/\\/frsfco.cvg.utn.edu.ar\\/user\\/profile.php?id=2564\",\"profileimageurl\":\"https:\\/\\/frsfco.cvg.utn.edu.ar\\/pluginfile.php\\/11225\\/user\\/icon\\/adaptable\\/f1?rev=710469\",\"profileimageurlsmall\":\"https:\\/\\/frsfco.cvg.utn.edu.ar\\/pluginfile.php\\/11225\\/user\\/icon\\/adaptable\\/f2?rev=710469\",\"isonline\":false,\"showonlinestatus\":true,\"isblocked\":false,\"iscontact\":false,\"isdeleted\":false,\"canmessageevenifblocked\":true,\"canmessage\":true,\"requirescontact\":false,\"cancreatecontact\":true,\"contactrequests\":[]}],\"messages\":[{\"id\":69212,\"useridfrom\":2564,\"text\":\"<p>Buenas noches Felipe. La fecha de recuperatorio siempre es la \\u00faltima semana de clases en noviembre. Se puede recuperar 1 s\\u00f3lo parcial. De acuerdo a tu nivel , no creo que tengas inconveniente para rendirlo. <br>\\nSaludos cordiales.<br>\\nSonia Dalmazzo.<\\/p>\",\"timecreated\":1688428216}],\"candeletemessagesforallusers\":false},{\"id\":19047,\"name\":\"\",\"subname\":null,\"imageurl\":null,\"type\":1,\"membercount\":2,\"ismuted\":false,\"isfavourite\":false,\"isread\":true,\"unreadcount\":null,\"members\":[{\"id\":2867,\"fullname\":\"Fernando Ezequiel Daniele\",\"profileurl\":\"https:\\/\\/frsfco.cvg.utn.edu.ar\\/user\\/profile.php?id=2867\",\"profileimageurl\":\"https:\\/\\/frsfco.cvg.utn.edu.ar\\/pluginfile.php\\/12716\\/user\\/icon\\/adaptable\\/f1?rev=1042165\",\"profileimageurlsmall\":\"https:\\/\\/frsfco.cvg.utn.edu.ar\\/pluginfile.php\\/12716\\/user\\/icon\\/adaptable\\/f2?rev=1042165\",\"isonline\":false,\"showonlinestatus\":true,\"isblocked\":false,\"iscontact\":false,\"isdeleted\":false,\"canmessageevenifblocked\":true,\"canmessage\":true,\"requirescontact\":false,\"cancreatecontact\":true,\"contactrequests\":[]}],\"messages\":[{\"id\":68796,\"useridfrom\":2867,\"text\":\"<p>Hola Felipe, ok no habr\\u00eda problema. Nos vemos a las 4<\\/p>\",\"timecreated\":1688002415}],\"candeletemessagesforallusers\":false},{\"id\":19189,\"name\":\"\",\"subname\":null,\"imageurl\":null,\"type\":1,\"membercount\":2,\"ismuted\":false,\"isfavourite\":false,\"isread\":true,\"unreadcount\":null,\"members\":[{\"id\":1072,\"fullname\":\"Hugo Pipino\",\"profileurl\":\"https:\\/\\/frsfco.cvg.utn.edu.ar\\/user\\/profile.php?id=1072\",\"profileimageurl\":\"https:\\/\\/frsfco.cvg.utn.edu.ar\\/theme\\/image.php\\/adaptable\\/core\\/1769817503\\/u\\/f1\",\"profileimageurlsmall\":\"https:\\/\\/frsfco.cvg.utn.edu.ar\\/theme\\/image.php\\/adaptable\\/core\\/1769817503\\/u\\/f2\",\"isonline\":false,\"showonlinestatus\":true,\"isblocked\":false,\"iscontact\":true,\"isdeleted\":false,\"canmessageevenifblocked\":true,\"canmessage\":true,\"requirescontact\":false,\"cancreatecontact\":true,\"contactrequests\":[]}],\"messages\":[{\"id\":65831,\"useridfrom\":1072,\"text\":\"<p>Es tambi\\u00e9n lo que plantearon en la segunda parte de la experiencia con la masa de 100 g colgada por dos cuerdas<\\/p>\",\"timecreated\":1684496207}],\"candeletemessagesforallusers\":false},{\"id\":17381,\"name\":\"\",\"subname\":null,\"imageurl\":null,\"type\":1,\"membercount\":2,\"ismuted\":false,\"isfavourite\":false,\"isread\":true,\"unreadcount\":null,\"members\":[{\"id\":2,\"fullname\":\"Admin Usuario\",\"profileurl\":\"https:\\/\\/frsfco.cvg.utn.edu.ar\\/user\\/profile.php?id=2\",\"profileimageurl\":\"https:\\/\\/frsfco.cvg.utn.edu.ar\\/pluginfile.php\\/8\\/user\\/icon\\/adaptable\\/f1?rev=1071784\",\"profileimageurlsmall\":\"https:\\/\\/frsfco.cvg.utn.edu.ar\\/pluginfile.php\\/8\\/user\\/icon\\/adaptable\\/f2?rev=1071784\",\"isonline\":true,\"showonlinestatus\":true,\"isblocked\":false,\"iscontact\":false,\"isdeleted\":false,\"canmessageevenifblocked\":true,\"canmessage\":false,\"requirescontact\":false,\"cancreatecontact\":false,\"contactrequests\":[]}],\"messages\":[{\"id\":62137,\"useridfrom\":2,\"text\":\"<p>Hola! buenas tardes! <br>\\nDesde la Oficina de Alumnos les recordamos que, quienes aprobaron el Seminario de Ingreso,  para formalizar la inscripci\\u00f3n a 1er a\\u00f1o deben subir la documentaci\\u00f3n solicitada al campus virtual. <br>\\nMuchas Gracias!<\\/p>\",\"timecreated\":1675889542}],\"candeletemessagesforallusers\":false}]}}]"
